ztodo version 0.2

A simple command-line todo list written in Go.

Installation:

1. Install Go:
    http://golang.org/doc/install.html

2. Install todo:
    $ go get github.com/jack-zh/ztodo

Usage:

    ztodo list|ls
        Show all tasks
    ztodo list|ls N
        Show task N
    ztodo rm|remove N
        Remove task N
    ztodo done N
        Done task N
    ztodo undo N
        Undo task N
    ztodo doing N
        Doing task N
    ztodo clean
        Rm done task
    ztodo clear
        Rm all task
    ztodo add ...
        Add task to list

Next version 0.3:

